igor:
	@rval=0; \
	for f in *.mdoc.in; do \
	    echo $(IGOR) -D $$f; \
	    $(IGOR) -D $$f || rval=`expr $$rval + $$?`; \
	done; \
	for f in $(OTHER_DOCS) $(OTHER_DOCS_LDAP); do \
	    case `basename $$f` in \
	    [A-Z][A-Z]*) \
		echo $(IGOR) -abrw $$f; \
		$(IGOR) -abrw $$f || rval=`expr $$rval + $$?`;; \
	    esac; \
	done; \
	exit $$rval
